subject: Soccer
UEFA Champions League (Soccer)
lead_paragraph: Real Madrid earned a 1-0 victory at Tottenham on Wednesday that moved it into the Champions League semifinals, and the defending champion Inter Milan was eliminated with a 2-1 loss at Schalke.
